---
import ResponsiveImage from './ResponsiveImage.astro';
---

<!-- Critical Information Section - Decision-Making Info Above Fold -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-24">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
        <span class="text-accent font-label uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs font-bold mb-4 block">EN ÇOK MERAK EDİLENLER</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6">Sık Aranan Konular</h2>
        <div class="h-0.5 w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent-light to-transparent mx-auto opacity-50"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-Column Grid with Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1: Eligibility -->
        <div class="group relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-700 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <!-- Card top image strip -->
            <div class="h-40 relative overflow-hidden">
                <ResponsiveImage src="/images/home/article-1.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width={400} height={160} loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white via-white/50 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled text-primary text-2xl">psychology</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 border-t-0 rounded-b-[2rem] p-8 lg:p-10">
                <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        İnfertilite Nedir?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
                        Kadın ve erkek infertilitesinin nedenleri, risk faktörleri ve ne zaman uzman desteği almanız gerektiğini bilimsel kaynaklarla açıklıyoruz.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/sorunlar" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
                        Rehberi Oku
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Pricing -->
        <div class="group relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-700 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="h-40 relative overflow-hidden">
                <ResponsiveImage src="/images/home/article-3.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width={400} height={160} loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white via-white/50 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-tertiary-container rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled text-tertiary text-2xl">biotech</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 border-t-0 rounded-b-[2rem] p-8 lg:p-10">
                <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        Tedavi Yöntemleri
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
                        IVF, ICSI, IUI, ovülasyon indüksiyonu ve cerrahi seçenekleri karşılaştırın. Hangi yöntem kime uygun? Başarı oranları nedir?
                    </p>
                    <a href="/tedavi-yontemleri" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
                        Yöntemleri Karşılaştır
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Timeline -->
        <div class="group relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-700 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="h-40 relative overflow-hidden">
                <ResponsiveImage src="/images/home/article-2.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width={400} height={160} loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white via-white/50 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-container rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled text-secondary text-2xl">labs</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 border-t-0 rounded-b-[2rem] p-8 lg:p-10">
                <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        Tanı Süreci
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
                        Hormon testleri, HSG, spermiogram ve genetik taramalar nasıl yorumlanır? Tanı algoritmasını adım adım öğrenin.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/tani-sureci" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
                        Tanı Rehberine Git
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
